rComments: Great professor! All the assignments were straightforward and the grading was fair. She was caring and very accomodating. If you want a good grade in the class, really read the material and engage that with the lectures becuase all the quizzes, discussions and exams are centered on the degree of your understanding of the material.

Dr. Ilea was by far one of the best professors I have had during my university experience. She focuses the students attention on the important details of the course which makes the class memorable and interesting. She does not over burdeing students unnecessarily. She was always available to help .

Adina Ilea is the best professor I have had during my 4 years at the University of Ottawa. She tought in a clear and detailed manner. She made the dry subject matter very enjoyable and memorable. She is also fair and approachable. I highly recommend taking any class she teaches.
